<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1912-02-05T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1912-02-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="1550" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1550">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 819.00/364.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Minister of Panama</gloss> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi>.</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">No. 4.]</seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Panama</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-02-05">
                                    <hi rend="italic">February 5, 1912</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Excellency</hi>: I have the honor to inform your
                            excellency that Señor Don Rodolfo Chiari assumed on the 1st day of this
                            month the Executive Power of the Republic of Panama in his capacity as
                            Third Designado, by reason of the leave granted the First Design a do in
                            Chargé of the Executive Power, Dr. Pablo Arosemena.</p>
                        <p>I have [etc.]</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Ricardo Arias.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>